
About - Thor Playground
===========================



Use - Thor Playground
====================

1. sudo gem install thor
2. git clone git://github.com/lcosta/thor-playground.git
3. cd thor-playground
4. thor t:t4 --force # test task "t:24" in file "thor-basic.thor"




Index
=====

1st - Part
----------

  * thor-basic.thor (rev. 2009-11-01 - lcosta)




